reviewText: This will be our THIRD girl to grow up with Miss Patty Cake.  We bought these to replace the VHS collection that we had and our new little one loves Miss Pattycake just as much as the others did.
My daughter loves this movie set so much that I bought one for each of my nieces for their birthdays.  All the girls absolutely love Miss Patty Cake and sing the songs all the time.

Toddlers love Miss Pattycake with all her songs and fun entertainment.  We love her and we this double feature is great.  My girls always like her a little more than the boys, but it is good toddler entertainment for both while teaching about God's great love.
